verbose_text: XREF_BIBR To calculate the mediation score, the following four models and equations were implemented :(Model 5) y ~ beta1A+ beta2A2+ beta3P+ beta4G+ beta5PxG+ epsilon, (Model 6) y ~ beta1E+ beta2A+ beta3A2+ beta4P+ beta5G+ beta6PxG+ epsilon, (Equation 2) Mediation_score = betaM5_5-betaM6_6betaM5_5, and (Equation 3) Z = betaM5_5xbetaM6_6betaM6_62xSM5_52+ betaM5_52xSM6_62, where y = trans gene expression, A = age, A 2 = age squared, E = cis gene expression, P = BMI, and G = cis genotype.
